We recommended that Management:
Initiate the termination of the contract or take-over of the work by administration or contract in accordance with Section 53.3 of the 2016 revised IRR of RA No. 9184;
Initiate measures and strategies to fast track the completion of the project such as provision of additional manpower and materials, and strict/close supervision of project works;
